title: El Chupacabra - Greenwood
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mission style Mexican food eatery and bar; this one is located on Phinney Ridge and can described as a punk rock cantina. Vegan could get rice, beans, and faux meat, and for an up-charge vegan cheese substitution in enchilada, burrito, taco, and tamale. Jukebox (free til 5pm), house made hot sauces, gluten free upon request.
